2026-05-18T19:45:38.3986188Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-18T19:45:38.3986958Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-18T19:45:38.3987744Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-18T19:45:38.3988669Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-18T19:45:38.3989798Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-18T19:45:38.3990692Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-18T19:45:38.3991448Z 255            preserve via tools:node="merge".
