2026-05-18T19:45:38.9969684Z 276            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-18T19:45:38.9970081Z 277            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-18T19:45:38.9970451Z 278            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
